{"tid":439532,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過所謂fasting排毒？","createTime":"2017-10-18T01:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T08:43:44.000Z","uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d2945996212953e333ea481b782036f5905d2453","tid":439532,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:39:25.000Z","msg":"fasting即係禁食，期間只飲水，目的並唔係減肥，千其唔好靠呢個方法減肥，減肥係靠均衡飲食，多菜少肉<br />\n<br />\n而禁食排毒個原理係唔食嘢48-72小時，頭廿四小時會消耗盡身體糖份去取得能量，廿四小時之後開始到消耗脂肪，最後先消耗肌肉入面啲蛋白質，因為人體長期以來食好多含毒素嘢，簡單到飲杯咖啡都有，加工食品又有，而毒素係鎖住嚮脂肪於各個器官，特別係肝臟，fasting個原理係令身體開始分解脂肪作能量，先可以將毒素釋放同排走<br />\n<br />\n其實兩日禁食應該多數人都頂得住，三日有啲難度"},{"pid":"8909e2a50f773b9b49295be0591091ddc798649d","tid":439532,"uid":65709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:46:54.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0731990d144ba96986b5e24af5041f3be98167d6","tid":439532,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:49:27.000Z","msg":"凡事循序漸進，試左初階版廿四小時先"},{"pid":"0520d85c50fcd38413411fdc4f2bfa6ac8af6758","tid":439532,"uid":25028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:51:53.000Z","msg":"有冇聽過腸胃炎排毒?"},{"pid":"6442251f948d1e5ff3e6786e993f1ba46520f3f0","tid":439532,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:52:15.000Z","msg":"依家keep住weekdays一日食一餐 皮膚好左好多"},{"pid":"e274c763e2bcaabceac5c52abad5e9b4e95b5627","tid":439532,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:56:10.000Z","msg":"有無科學根據?"},{"pid":"99e2de78c9aa870e5044020cd6b292de84054c89","tid":439532,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇聽過腸胃炎排毒?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf490a0a5694f1c405b28683d3857454ea5a1a0","tid":439532,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:59:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無科學根據?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消耗糖、脂肪、蛋白質呢個次序絕對科學，但可以排走幾多毒我就唔敢講，都係睇健康網站睇返黎"},{"pid":"49bb8594a4528a9bd97c0c08ef29cf741a5f7d1b","tid":439532,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:59:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無科學根據?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有 不過未發展到好完整<br />\nsearch intermittent fasting"},{"pid":"045f27efee9719d61afb07246a675ae86a6a2ca4","tid":439532,"uid":68046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:33:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無科學根據?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消耗糖、脂肪、蛋白質呢個次序絕對科學，但可以排走幾多毒我就唔敢講，都係睇健康網站睇返黎</blockquote><br />\n又係內容農場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2048e83d25e8e3a122e2c2ee9f41cf00e3ccfccc","tid":439532,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:11:22.000Z","msg":"無用, 要食嘢條腸先會濡動"},{"pid":"1e312cba6da2c775b3589b77bdd913f7eda64210","tid":439532,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇聽過腸胃炎排毒?</blockquote><br />\n萬試萬靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f080802e8363de6408d778a168209abd2436455","tid":439532,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:30:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無用, 要食嘢條腸先會濡動</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n排毒唔一定係痾屎"},{"pid":"a16310fd2d1681309223ba178fbb8ff52e4b33e9","tid":439532,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:09:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無用, 要食嘢條腸先會濡動</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n排毒唔一定係痾屎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9e3fd079c9844bf2e06a4b455c0edc768229f3","tid":439532,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:47:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無用, 要食嘢條腸先會濡動</blockquote